- Validate LDAP+SSL support
- Validate LDAP+STARTTLS support
- Add support for CA and client certificates
- Add support for role attributes:
  - SUPERUSER
  - CREATEDB
  - CREATEROLE
  - NOINHERIT
  - BYPASSRLS
  - CONNECTION LIMIT
- Add support for allowing arbitrary GUCs to be set
- Add support for including login roles in one or more group roles
- Add support for syncing group roles and their membership from LDAP
- Allow LDAP filtering to be configured (and include AD example for users)